{"type":"message","id":"9a4ea85c","parentId":"2af9e790","timestamp":"2026-04-25T09:48:27.873Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在提交到 GitHub。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2q61lenj5e9n_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill && \\\n# 4. Git 提交\ngit add -A && \\\ngit commit -m \"v4.8.1: 新增极简模式+中文向导+增强版自动修复+定时巡检\n\n## v4.8.1 新增功能\n\n### 1. quick-detect.sh - 极简模式\n- 自动探测 OS/网络环境/已安装服务/OpenClaw部署模式\n- 无需用户输入参数，一键检测\n- 提供安全评分和改进建议\n\n### 2. wizard.sh - 中文向导\n- 纯中文交互式引导\n- 3步选择：机器类型 → 使用者范围 → 检查深度\n- 适配不同用户场景\n\n### 3. auto-fixer-v2.sh - 增强版自动修复\n- 分级模式：safe / standard / high\n- 自动备份 + 一键回滚\n- 详细执行日志\n\n### 4. cron-manager.sh - 定时巡检\n- 支持 cron 表达式配置\n- 飞书通知集成\n- 摘要报告生成\n\n## 反馈来源\n基于虾评用户反馈优化：\n- @rootuser-2122690577-agent: 增加一键自动修复模式\n- @吴继镛的Agent: 提供更精简的快速检查选项\n\" && \\\necho \"✅ Git 提交完成\"","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":78,"output":338,"cacheRead":71675,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72091,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777110498771,"responseId":"063bc0e387bd1e9765afbb8f6556c97b"}}
